{"questionId":"3470973","questionHtml":"<p>Perform the test and give your conclusion in context.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>EITHER</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math>-<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>value</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>0629</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>0629034</mn><mo>…</mo><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A2</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>0629</mn><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>05</mn></math> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong> R1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><msup><mi>χ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>calc</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>30</mn></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>A2</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>7</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>30</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>82</mn></math> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong> R1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A2</strong></em> for either <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math>-<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>value</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>063</mn></math>&nbsp;or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><msup><mi>χ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>calc</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>3</mn></math> seen. Award <em><strong>R1</strong></em> for a correct comparison involve their <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math>-<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>value</mi></math> or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><msup><mi>χ</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mi>calc</mi></msub></math>, and follow through for their conclusion.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>THEN</strong></p>\n<p>so there is insufficient evidence to reject <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">H</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math>, i.e.</p>\n<p>there is no particular preference for any of the flavours. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong> A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Do not award <em><strong>R0A1.</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[4 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"3470973","referenceCode":"23M.1.AHL.TZ2.10b","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Perform the test and give your conclusion in context.","paper":"1","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","SL 4.11—Expected, observed, hypotheses, chi squared, gof, t-test"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}